      "releaseNotes": "Mono Lab 3.3 - 3 new filters, 6 optimized\n\nDither Press - Tone decomposition filter with three distinct modes.\nOverlight - Live animated luminance filter. Highlights shimmer and breathe with two animation modes.\nLines - Vertical polyline displacement filter flows around the contours of your photo, creating a warped wireframe-like interpretation.\n\nOptimized:\nDot Field - Digital stippling filter\nBitmap Ghost - Destroyed bitmap print simulation\nMoiré Drift - Live animated moiré interference pattern with optical shimmer and tonal displacement\nVelvet Phase - Smooth, rich grayscale tonal filter\nHollow Tone - Edge-focused tonal filter with adjustable edge retention",
